The reasone we did 14 bit shift is, because in the pdf there was a mention(page 7) that the data is 18 bit precision so we did (32-18)=14 bit shift : https://cdn-shop.adafruit.com/product-files/3421/i2S+Datasheet.PDF

Also in page no 7, there is a mention of 24 bit data format. and 32-24=8. Basicallz we were trzing out stuff 

